  "detailed_description": "Fish Hero is a physics, parkour adventure! Launch yourself up a collection of biomes to reach the summit. Compete against friends by pushing them off platforms to throw them off course. Explore a unique world as a fish out of water.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Climb!</strong></h2><br>It's a long road ahead, you better get your big fish boots on and start climbing with or without Friends! you'll need to get used to the fish's flop to succeed. It may take a few too many falls keep in mind...<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2898650/extras/5331e114912ddcad9ba01f57a8a91cc1.poster.avif?t=1722611664\" width=800 height=276 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2898650/extras/5331e114912ddcad9ba01f57a8a91cc1.webm?t=1722611664\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2898650/extras/5331e114912ddcad9ba01f57a8a91cc1.mp4?t=1722611664\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Fall!</strong></h2><br>Oh and it won't be easy. You can only place one checkpoint at any time making for a risky journey. luckily there are some nets placed by fisherman to catch your fall (if you're lucky)<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2898650/extras/7b296363b97e5e5f95719d8bfb20ad7b.poster.avif?t=1722611664\" width=800 height=276 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2898650/extras/7b296363b97e5e5f95719d8bfb20ad7b.webm?t=1722611664\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2898650/extras/7b296363b97e5e5f95719d8bfb20ad7b.mp4?t=1722611664\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Developer Note</h2><br>I've been a big fan of the Foddian-like genre, I decided to create one myself but make sure there's the added fun of multiplayer. I thought about hundreds of fish climbing a huge level in sync. Therefore Fish Hero needed to be made before I could rest. Try and beat it and tweet at me @HENRY_MEAD_<br><br>Thanks! Have Fun Falling!",
  "about_the_game": "Fish Hero is a physics, parkour adventure! Launch yourself up a collection of biomes to reach the summit. Compete against friends by pushing them off platforms to throw them off course. Explore a unique world as a fish out of water.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Climb!</strong></h2><br>It's a long road ahead, you better get your big fish boots on and start climbing with or without Friends! you'll need to get used to the fish's flop to succeed. It may take a few too many falls keep in mind...<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2898650/extras/5331e114912ddcad9ba01f57a8a91cc1.poster.avif?t=1722611664\" width=800 height=276 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2898650/extras/5331e114912ddcad9ba01f57a8a91cc1.webm?t=1722611664\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2898650/extras/5331e114912ddcad9ba01f57a8a91cc1.mp4?t=1722611664\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Fall!</strong></h2><br>Oh and it won't be easy. You can only place one checkpoint at any time making for a risky journey. luckily there are some nets placed by fisherman to catch your fall (if you're lucky)<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2898650/extras/7b296363b97e5e5f95719d8bfb20ad7b.poster.avif?t=1722611664\" width=800 height=276 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2898650/extras/7b296363b97e5e5f95719d8bfb20ad7b.webm?t=1722611664\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2898650/extras/7b296363b97e5e5f95719d8bfb20ad7b.mp4?t=1722611664\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Developer Note</h2><br>I've been a big fan of the Foddian-like genre, I decided to create one myself but make sure there's the added fun of multiplayer. I thought about hundreds of fish climbing a huge level in sync. Therefore Fish Hero needed to be made before I could rest. Try and beat it and tweet at me @HENRY_MEAD_<br><br>Thanks! Have Fun Falling!",
